OL,5,
OL,6,GBBC Northern Ireland's main local news
OL,7,Gprogramme, BBC Newsline, launched a new
OL,8,Glook today.
OL,10,
OL,11,FToday's breakfast and lunchtime
OL,12,Fprogrammes were broadcast from the
OL,13,Ftemporary set in Studio 1 at
OL,14,FBroadcasting House in Belfast. The
OL,15,Ftemporary facility has been in use
OL,16,Fsince August, whilst construction and
OL,17,Ftechnical testing of the new set-up in
OL,18,FStudio B was in progress.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
OL,22,                                   G1/4
