OL,5,
OL,6,FThe updated set in Studio B was
OL,7,Frevealed on air at 6.30pm. It's based
OL,8,Fon the design and technology used in
OL,9,FStudio B at New Broadcasting House in
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe Belfast set-up includes a desk, a
OL,14,Fmonolith video tower and a large
OL,15,Frectangular videowall.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
