OL,5,
OL,6,FStudio B retains its green screen
OL,7,Ffacility which adjoins the main
OL,8,Fphysical set. A virtual set is used for
OL,9,Fthe sports segment within the 6.30pm
OL,10,Fweekday programme.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe weather presenter utilises a large
OL,14,Fsection of the main videowall for the
OL,15,Fweather forecast at the end of the
OL,16,F6.30pm programme. All other weather
OL,17,Felements (including during the 6.30pm
OL,18,Fopening headlines) are based in the
OL,19,Fsmall Studio C green screen facility.
